servinfo.title: Injection Warning Light Remains ON after Engine Start

servinfosub.title: Wiring Diagram
servinfosub.ptxt: Refer to Immobilizer Control System Wiring Circuit Diagram .

servinfosub.title: Circuit Description
servinfosub.ptxt: When ECM has any DTC(s), injection warning light remains ON after engine starts.

servinfosub.title: Troubleshooting
servinfosub.ptxt: Check ECM for DTC(s) referring to DTC Check and then, go to applicable DTC diag. flow.
